spec_data.Name: perl-MooseX-Meta-TypeConstraint-ForceCoercion
spec_data.Description:
This class allows to wrap any Moose::Meta::TypeConstraint in a way that
will force coercion of the value when checking or validating a value
against it.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:56:43 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Force coercion when validating type constraints
